OL,3,CSecond man charged after discovery of
OL,4,Cmissing man's remains
OL,6,FA second man has been charged
OL,7,Ffollowing the discovery of a murder
OL,8,Fvictim's remains six years after he
OL,9,Fwent missing.
OL,11,FThe body of 55-year-old Richard Dyson,
OL,12,Fwho was last seen alive in 2019, was
OL,13,Ffound at a property in Broadcarr Road
OL,14,Fin Barnsley last July.
OL,16,FTests confirmed he died of shotgun
OL,17,Fwounds.
