OL,3,CSecond man charged after discovery of
OL,4,Cmissing man's remains
OL,6,FChristopher Wright, 72, from Hoyland,
OL,7,Fwas charged with Mr Dyson's murder in
OL,8,FNovember last year. He was also
OL,9,Fcharged with preventing a lawful and
OL,10,Fdecent burial and 27 firearms offences
OL,11,Fincluding possessing a banned weapon
OL,12,Fand possessing firearms without a
OL,13,Fcertificate.
OL,15,FKarl Schwalbe, who is also 72, from
OL,16,FRotherham, has now been charged with
OL,17,Fconspiracy to pervert the court of
OL,18,Fjustice and has been remanded in
OL,19,Fcustody.
