OL,3,CSecond man charged after discovery of
OL,4,Cmissing man's remains
OL,6,FHe was due to appear at Barnsley's
OL,7,FMagistrates Court on Tuesday.
OL,9,FMr Dyson was last seen by his daughter
OL,10,Fon 15 November 2019.
OL,12,FTwo days later he was seen walking
OL,13,Falong the A6135 Sheffield Road in
OL,14,FHoyland but then disappeared. His
OL,15,Fremains were found on 14 July.
